      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TODD KEEPING (3) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by 4 lengths at this track in a handy 22.56 beating Carry On Olive. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Can continue the winning form. CARRY ON NATASHA (2) comes into this as a quickest on the card winner last time at this track, scoring by 3 lengths (22.47). Looks suited and is one of the contenders. MAZUMA MAYHEM (1) turned in a plain run last time when fifth at Murray Bridge over 395m behind Minnie's My Mum (22.74) in a Grade 3/4/5. Was in the money the start prior. The form from his last run stacks up well. Has ability and is one of the better chances. LOVING IT SWEET (7) is worth including.",
